{"problem":{"stackLimit":128,"modifiedUser":"root","auth":1,"isRemote":false,"description":"<p>假设有N盏灯(N为不大于5000的正整数)，从1到N按顺序依次编号，初始时全部处于开启状态；有M个人(M为不大于N的正整数)也从1到M依次编号。<p><p>第一个人(1号)将灯全部关闭，第二个人(2号)将编号为2的倍数的灯打开，第三个人(3号)将编号为3的倍数的灯做相反处理（即将打开的灯关闭，将关闭的灯打开）。依照编号递增顺序，以后的人都和3号一样，将凡是自己编号倍数的灯做相反处理。<p><p>请问：当第M个人操作之后，哪几盏灯是关闭的，按从小到大输出其编号，其间用逗号间隔。<p>","removeEndBlank":true,"uploadCase":true,"source":"","remote":false,"title":"开关灯 ","type":0,"difficulty":1,"output":"<p>顺次输出关闭的灯的编号，其间用逗号间隔。<p>","timeLimit":1000,"input":"<p>输入正整数N和M，以单个空格隔开。<p>","examples":"<input>10 10\n</input><output>1,4,9\n</output>","ioScore":10000,"codeShare":false,"hint":"","isRemoveEndBlank":true,"openCaseResult":true,"memoryLimit":256,"problemId":"T1109","isUploadCase":true},"languages":["C","C With O2","C++","C++ With O2","Java","Python3","Python2","Golang","C#"],"codeTemplates":[],"isSpj":false,"samples":[{"output":"1.out","input":"1.in","score":100},{"output":"2.out","input":"2.in","score":100},{"output":"3.out","input":"3.in","score":100},{"output":"4.out","input":"4.in","score":100},{"output":"5.out","input":"5.in","score":100},{"output":"6.out","input":"6.in","score":100},{"output":"7.out","input":"7.in","score":100},{"output":"8.out","input":"8.in","score":100},{"output":"9.out","input":"9.in","score":100},{"output":"10.out","input":"10.in","score":100}],"tags":["一本通在线评测"]}